{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u7014d1c3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性都是重要的安全机制，但它们防御的攻击类型和作用方式不同：</span></p><hr id=\"KCVcB\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"GOuZV\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. HttpOnly 属性</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub3a8eac6\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">作用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：禁止客户端的 JavaScript 脚本通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">document.cookie</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 读取或修改该 Cookie。</span></li><li id=\"u3a834061\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">目的</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防御跨站脚本攻击（XSS）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。即使攻击者通过 XSS 注入了恶意脚本，也无法窃取标记为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 Cookie（如会话令牌），从而保护用户登录态。</span></li><li id=\"ub204dabd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">使用场景</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：通常用于存储身份认证信息的 Cookie（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">sessionId</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），确保它们只能由浏览器自动发送给服务器，而无法被前端代码访问。</span></li><li id=\"u19bfdfab\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; HttpOnly</span></code></li></ul><hr id=\"iRhXr\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"wSMb8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. SameSite 属性</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ubbb160ee\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">作用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：控制 Cookie 在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">跨站请求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（cross-site requests）中是否被发送。</span></li><li id=\"uda9a1ad4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">目的</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防御跨站请求伪造（CSRF）攻击</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。通过限制第三方网站发起的请求携带 Cookie，使攻击者无法伪造用户的认证请求。</span></li><li id=\"u65dc36bb\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">可选值</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8b6eea41\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Strict</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：最严格，仅当请求来自同站时发送 Cookie。跨站请求（如用户点击恶意链接）均不携带。</span></li><li id=\"u23f8eb94\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Lax</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：默认值（现代浏览器）。允许部分安全跨站请求携带 Cookie（如链接跳转的 GET 请求），但阻止 POST、PUT 等可能修改数据的请求。</span></li><li id=\"uea5ed66e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：允许所有跨站请求携带 Cookie，但必须同时设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Secure</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性（仅 HTTPS 发送），适用于需要跨域共享 Cookie 的场景（如单点登录）。</span></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u9bd24625\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; SameSite=Lax</span></code></li></ul><hr id=\"PHOiV\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"UIVwH\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u861734e9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 保护 Cookie 不被脚本窃取（XSS 防御）。  </span></li><li id=\"u6ff08ad7\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 保护 Cookie 不被跨站恶意利用（CSRF 防御）。<br />两者结合使用，可以显著提升 Web 应用的安全性，是现代 Web 应用配置 Cookie 的标准实践。</span></li></ul></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u7014d1c3\" id=\"u7014d1c3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2258c57c\" id=\"u2258c57c\">Cookie 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ueba797ec\" id=\"ueba797ec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5e83b848\" id=\"u5e83b848\">HttpOnly</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u32798064\" id=\"u32798064\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u110e2f92\" id=\"u110e2f92\"><span data-lake-id=\"u61764a12\" id=\"u61764a12\">SameSite</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u918aef82\" id=\"u918aef82\"> 属性都是重要的安全机制，但它们防御的攻击类型和作用方式不同：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22KCVcB%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"GOuZV\" id=\"GOuZV\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba2e27e3\" id=\"uba2e27e3\">1. HttpOnly 属性</span></h3><ul list=\"u6c4d3e9b\"><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"ub3a8eac6\" id=\"ub3a8eac6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7ac28925\" id=\"u7ac28925\">作用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue232f58e\" id=\"ue232f58e\">：禁止客户端的 JavaScript 脚本通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u05fb3582\" id=\"u05fb3582\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub3b0213a\" id=\"ub3b0213a\">document.cookie</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udaa2dfb6\" id=\"udaa2dfb6\"> 读取或修改该 Cookie。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"u3a834061\" id=\"u3a834061\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u76ea45cb\" id=\"u76ea45cb\">目的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3fdeb3cd\" id=\"u3fdeb3cd\">：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2f540025\" id=\"u2f540025\">防御跨站脚本攻击（XSS）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubdd2a01f\" id=\"ubdd2a01f\">。即使攻击者通过 XSS 注入了恶意脚本，也无法窃取标记为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc78b0445\" id=\"uc78b0445\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubd0fb472\" id=\"ubd0fb472\">HttpOnly</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u893f7a12\" id=\"u893f7a12\"> 的 Cookie（如会话令牌），从而保护用户登录态。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"ub204dabd\" id=\"ub204dabd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8c7ce526\" id=\"u8c7ce526\">使用场景</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u69dec565\" id=\"u69dec565\">：通常用于存储身份认证信息的 Cookie（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubd781075\" id=\"ubd781075\"><span data-lake-id=\"u749308eb\" id=\"u749308eb\">sessionId</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ube802ad0\" id=\"ube802ad0\">），确保它们只能由浏览器自动发送给服务器，而无法被前端代码访问。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"u19bfdfab\" id=\"u19bfdfab\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8a9190c3\" id=\"u8a9190c3\">设置方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud8916027\" id=\"ud8916027\">：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u7b13a467\" id=\"u7b13a467\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf1a8ea57\" id=\"uf1a8ea57\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; HttpOnly</span></code></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22iRhXr%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"wSMb8\" id=\"wSMb8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u684ab4b8\" id=\"u684ab4b8\">2. SameSite 属性</span></h3><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\"><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"ubbb160ee\" id=\"ubbb160ee\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udc010918\" id=\"udc010918\">作用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u868cef8e\" id=\"u868cef8e\">：控制 Cookie 在</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua307848c\" id=\"ua307848c\">跨站请求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u33077f1a\" id=\"u33077f1a\">（cross-site requests）中是否被发送。</span></li><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"uda9a1ad4\" id=\"uda9a1ad4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5be3abec\" id=\"u5be3abec\">目的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub0a59389\" id=\"ub0a59389\">：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc275a41c\" id=\"uc275a41c\">防御跨站请求伪造（CSRF）攻击</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uee04d38a\" id=\"uee04d38a\">。通过限制第三方网站发起的请求携带 Cookie，使攻击者无法伪造用户的认证请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"u65dc36bb\" id=\"u65dc36bb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u06fa5b00\" id=\"u06fa5b00\">可选值</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2d69b99\" id=\"ub2d69b99\">：</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"u8b6eea41\" id=\"u8b6eea41\"><code data-lake-id=\"u751aa6f0\" id=\"u751aa6f0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5588d006\" id=\"u5588d006\">Strict</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uce3e690f\" id=\"uce3e690f\">：最严格，仅当请求来自同站时发送 Cookie。跨站请求（如用户点击恶意链接）均不携带。</span></li><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"u23f8eb94\" id=\"u23f8eb94\"><code data-lake-id=\"u6f0927b7\" id=\"u6f0927b7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a4aa0b8\" id=\"u3a4aa0b8\">Lax</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u24deae5a\" id=\"u24deae5a\">：默认值（现代浏览器）。允许部分安全跨站请求携带 Cookie（如链接跳转的 GET 请求），但阻止 POST、PUT 等可能修改数据的请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"uea5ed66e\" id=\"uea5ed66e\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua96641f8\" id=\"ua96641f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u03e5188b\" id=\"u03e5188b\">None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uad6d0e1b\" id=\"uad6d0e1b\">：允许所有跨站请求携带 Cookie，但必须同时设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud0a91b42\" id=\"ud0a91b42\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1571f0ce\" id=\"u1571f0ce\">Secure</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u66e4e07c\" id=\"u66e4e07c\"> 属性（仅 HTTPS 发送），适用于需要跨域共享 Cookie 的场景（如单点登录）。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\" start=\"4\"><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"u9bd24625\" id=\"u9bd24625\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4712d0f9\" id=\"u4712d0f9\">设置方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u529784f9\" id=\"u529784f9\">：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u65937cfd\" id=\"u65937cfd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5fb6528d\" id=\"u5fb6528d\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; SameSite=Lax</span></code></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22PHOiV%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"UIVwH\" id=\"UIVwH\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6e202f98\" id=\"u6e202f98\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"u7dcb89fd\"><li fid=\"u7a29bb44\" data-lake-id=\"u861734e9\" id=\"u861734e9\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u17374696\" id=\"u17374696\">HttpOnly</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u08b3d1d6\" id=\"u08b3d1d6\"> 保护 Cookie 不被脚本窃取（XSS 防御）。  </span></li><li fid=\"u7a29bb44\" data-lake-id=\"u6ff08ad7\" id=\"u6ff08ad7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0ae11f2a\" id=\"u0ae11f2a\">SameSite</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub9c88099\" id=\"ub9c88099\"> 保护 Cookie 不被跨站恶意利用（CSRF 防御）。<br />两者结合使用，可以显著提升 Web 应用的安全性，是现代 Web 应用配置 Cookie 的标准实践。</span></li></ul>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u7014d1c3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Cookie 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性都是重要的安全机制，但它们防御的攻击类型和作用方式不同：</span></p><hr id=\"KCVcB\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"GOuZV\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. HttpOnly 属性</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub3a8eac6\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">作用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：禁止客户端的 JavaScript 脚本通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">document.cookie</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 读取或修改该 Cookie。</span></li><li id=\"u3a834061\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">目的</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防御跨站脚本攻击（XSS）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。即使攻击者通过 XSS 注入了恶意脚本，也无法窃取标记为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 Cookie（如会话令牌），从而保护用户登录态。</span></li><li id=\"ub204dabd\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">使用场景</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：通常用于存储身份认证信息的 Cookie（如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">sessionId</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">），确保它们只能由浏览器自动发送给服务器，而无法被前端代码访问。</span></li><li id=\"u19bfdfab\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; HttpOnly</span></code></li></ul><hr id=\"iRhXr\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"wSMb8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. SameSite 属性</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ubbb160ee\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">作用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：控制 Cookie 在</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">跨站请求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（cross-site requests）中是否被发送。</span></li><li id=\"uda9a1ad4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">目的</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">防御跨站请求伪造（CSRF）攻击</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。通过限制第三方网站发起的请求携带 Cookie，使攻击者无法伪造用户的认证请求。</span></li><li id=\"u65dc36bb\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">可选值</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8b6eea41\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Strict</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：最严格，仅当请求来自同站时发送 Cookie。跨站请求（如用户点击恶意链接）均不携带。</span></li><li id=\"u23f8eb94\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Lax</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：默认值（现代浏览器）。允许部分安全跨站请求携带 Cookie（如链接跳转的 GET 请求），但阻止 POST、PUT 等可能修改数据的请求。</span></li><li id=\"uea5ed66e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">None</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：允许所有跨站请求携带 Cookie，但必须同时设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Secure</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性（仅 HTTPS 发送），适用于需要跨域共享 Cookie 的场景（如单点登录）。</span></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u9bd24625\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">设置方式</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; SameSite=Lax</span></code></li></ul><hr id=\"PHOiV\" class=\"ne-hr\"><h3 id=\"UIVwH\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u861734e9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">HttpOnly</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 保护 Cookie 不被脚本窃取（XSS 防御）。  </span></li><li id=\"u6ff08ad7\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">SameSite</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 保护 Cookie 不被跨站恶意利用（CSRF 防御）。<br />两者结合使用，可以显著提升 Web 应用的安全性，是现代 Web 应用配置 Cookie 的标准实践。</span></li></ul></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u7014d1c3\" id=\"u7014d1c3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2258c57c\" id=\"u2258c57c\">Cookie 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ueba797ec\" id=\"ueba797ec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5e83b848\" id=\"u5e83b848\">HttpOnly</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u32798064\" id=\"u32798064\"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u110e2f92\" id=\"u110e2f92\"><span data-lake-id=\"u61764a12\" id=\"u61764a12\">SameSite</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u918aef82\" id=\"u918aef82\"> 属性都是重要的安全机制，但它们防御的攻击类型和作用方式不同：</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22KCVcB%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"GOuZV\" id=\"GOuZV\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba2e27e3\" id=\"uba2e27e3\">1. HttpOnly 属性</span></h3><ul list=\"u6c4d3e9b\"><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"ub3a8eac6\" id=\"ub3a8eac6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7ac28925\" id=\"u7ac28925\">作用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue232f58e\" id=\"ue232f58e\">：禁止客户端的 JavaScript 脚本通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u05fb3582\" id=\"u05fb3582\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub3b0213a\" id=\"ub3b0213a\">document.cookie</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udaa2dfb6\" id=\"udaa2dfb6\"> 读取或修改该 Cookie。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"u3a834061\" id=\"u3a834061\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u76ea45cb\" id=\"u76ea45cb\">目的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3fdeb3cd\" id=\"u3fdeb3cd\">：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2f540025\" id=\"u2f540025\">防御跨站脚本攻击（XSS）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubdd2a01f\" id=\"ubdd2a01f\">。即使攻击者通过 XSS 注入了恶意脚本，也无法窃取标记为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc78b0445\" id=\"uc78b0445\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubd0fb472\" id=\"ubd0fb472\">HttpOnly</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u893f7a12\" id=\"u893f7a12\"> 的 Cookie（如会话令牌），从而保护用户登录态。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"ub204dabd\" id=\"ub204dabd\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8c7ce526\" id=\"u8c7ce526\">使用场景</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u69dec565\" id=\"u69dec565\">：通常用于存储身份认证信息的 Cookie（如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubd781075\" id=\"ubd781075\"><span data-lake-id=\"u749308eb\" id=\"u749308eb\">sessionId</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ube802ad0\" id=\"ube802ad0\">），确保它们只能由浏览器自动发送给服务器，而无法被前端代码访问。</span></li><li fid=\"u2d5ba503\" data-lake-id=\"u19bfdfab\" id=\"u19bfdfab\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8a9190c3\" id=\"u8a9190c3\">设置方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud8916027\" id=\"ud8916027\">：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u7b13a467\" id=\"u7b13a467\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf1a8ea57\" id=\"uf1a8ea57\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; HttpOnly</span></code></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22iRhXr%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"wSMb8\" id=\"wSMb8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u684ab4b8\" id=\"u684ab4b8\">2. SameSite 属性</span></h3><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\"><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"ubbb160ee\" id=\"ubbb160ee\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udc010918\" id=\"udc010918\">作用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u868cef8e\" id=\"u868cef8e\">：控制 Cookie 在</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua307848c\" id=\"ua307848c\">跨站请求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u33077f1a\" id=\"u33077f1a\">（cross-site requests）中是否被发送。</span></li><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"uda9a1ad4\" id=\"uda9a1ad4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5be3abec\" id=\"u5be3abec\">目的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub0a59389\" id=\"ub0a59389\">：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc275a41c\" id=\"uc275a41c\">防御跨站请求伪造（CSRF）攻击</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uee04d38a\" id=\"uee04d38a\">。通过限制第三方网站发起的请求携带 Cookie，使攻击者无法伪造用户的认证请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"u65dc36bb\" id=\"u65dc36bb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u06fa5b00\" id=\"u06fa5b00\">可选值</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2d69b99\" id=\"ub2d69b99\">：</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"u8b6eea41\" id=\"u8b6eea41\"><code data-lake-id=\"u751aa6f0\" id=\"u751aa6f0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5588d006\" id=\"u5588d006\">Strict</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uce3e690f\" id=\"uce3e690f\">：最严格，仅当请求来自同站时发送 Cookie。跨站请求（如用户点击恶意链接）均不携带。</span></li><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"u23f8eb94\" id=\"u23f8eb94\"><code data-lake-id=\"u6f0927b7\" id=\"u6f0927b7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a4aa0b8\" id=\"u3a4aa0b8\">Lax</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u24deae5a\" id=\"u24deae5a\">：默认值（现代浏览器）。允许部分安全跨站请求携带 Cookie（如链接跳转的 GET 请求），但阻止 POST、PUT 等可能修改数据的请求。</span></li><li fid=\"u51902866\" data-lake-id=\"uea5ed66e\" id=\"uea5ed66e\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua96641f8\" id=\"ua96641f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u03e5188b\" id=\"u03e5188b\">None</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uad6d0e1b\" id=\"uad6d0e1b\">：允许所有跨站请求携带 Cookie，但必须同时设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud0a91b42\" id=\"ud0a91b42\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1571f0ce\" id=\"u1571f0ce\">Secure</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u66e4e07c\" id=\"u66e4e07c\"> 属性（仅 HTTPS 发送），适用于需要跨域共享 Cookie 的场景（如单点登录）。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u9dd1755f\" start=\"4\"><li fid=\"u786d14ce\" data-lake-id=\"u9bd24625\" id=\"u9bd24625\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4712d0f9\" id=\"u4712d0f9\">设置方式</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u529784f9\" id=\"u529784f9\">：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u65937cfd\" id=\"u65937cfd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5fb6528d\" id=\"u5fb6528d\">Set-Cookie: sessionId=abc123; SameSite=Lax</span></code></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22PHOiV%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"UIVwH\" id=\"UIVwH\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6e202f98\" id=\"u6e202f98\">总结</span></h3><ul list=\"u7dcb89fd\"><li fid=\"u7a29bb44\" data-lake-id=\"u861734e9\" id=\"u861734e9\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u17374696\" id=\"u17374696\">HttpOnly</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u08b3d1d6\" id=\"u08b3d1d6\"> 保护 Cookie 不被脚本窃取（XSS 防御）。  </span></li><li fid=\"u7a29bb44\" data-lake-id=\"u6ff08ad7\" id=\"u6ff08ad7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0ae11f2a\" id=\"u0ae11f2a\">SameSite</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub9c88099\" id=\"ub9c88099\"> 保护 Cookie 不被跨站恶意利用（CSRF 防御）。<br />两者结合使用，可以显著提升 Web 应用的安全性，是现代 Web 应用配置 Cookie 的标准实践。</span></li></ul>","word_count":491,"slug":"hmvkxkhm1sx09pqs","type":"Doc","title":"Cookie 的 SameSite 属性、HttpOnly 属性分别有什么作用？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"Cookie 的 HttpOnly 和 SameSite 属性都是重要的安全机制，但它们防御的攻击类型和作用方式不同：1. HttpOnly 属性作用：禁止客户端的 JavaScript 脚本通过 document.cookie 读取或修改该 Cookie。目的：防御跨站脚本攻击（XSS）。即...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"hr\":3}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-26T08:02:52.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-26T08:03:54.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-26T08:03:53.700Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-26T08:03:54.000Z","id":258003292},"doc_digest":"V13rj3cwclAAzEgE8cyrstUoXCU"}